### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@masterKey = miClaveMaestraSegura123!

### 1. Crear nueva entrada de contraseña
POST {{baseUrl}}/password-manager
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Gmail Personal",
  "description": "Cuenta principal de Gmail",
  "username": "usuario@gmail.com",
  "password": "miContraseñaSegura123!",
  "url": "https://gmail.com",
  "category": "Email",
  "notes": "Cuenta creada en 2020",
  "masterKey": "{{masterKey}}"
}

### 2. Crear otra entrada de contraseña
POST {{baseUrl}}/password-manager
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Facebook",
  "description": "Red social personal",
  "username": "usuario@facebook.com",
  "password": "otraContraseñaSegura456!",
  "url": "https://facebook.com",
  "category": "Redes Sociales",
  "notes": "Perfil personal",
  "masterKey": "{{masterKey}}"
}

### 3. Obtener todas las entradas
GET {{baseUrl}}/password-manager

### 4. Obtener entrada específica
GET {{baseUrl}}/password-manager/1

### 5. Obtener entradas por categoría
GET {{baseUrl}}/password-manager/category/Email

### 6. Descifrar contraseña
POST {{baseUrl}}/password-manager/1/decrypt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "masterKey": "{{masterKey}}"
}

### 7. Actualizar entrada
PUT {{baseUrl}}/password-manager/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Gmail Personal Actualizado",
  "description": "Cuenta principal de Gmail - Actualizada",
  "masterKey": "{{masterKey}}"
}

### 8. Eliminar entrada
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/password-manager/1?masterKey={{masterKey}}

### 9. Probar con clave maestra incorrecta
POST {{baseUrl}}/password-manager/2/decrypt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "masterKey": "claveIncorrecta"
}
